Every fixture method that accepts a `[Timeout]` attribute has an equivalent global configuration setting. Configure timeouts globally through [runsettings](unit-testing-mstest-configure#mstest-element) or [testconfig.json](unit-testing-mstest-configure#timeout-settings) using settings like `TestInitializeTimeout`, `ClassInitializeTimeout`, `AssemblyInitializ

